message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been meticulously designed and crafted to meet your needs. This product holds significant value for me, but I understand its worth might vary based on your specific requirements. I am offering it to you for $120, which I believe strikes a balance between its intrinsic value and your perceived worth. Don't hesitate to let me know if this offer meets your expectations or if you need more information about the product.
